00:06:35.580 --> 00:06:38.720 align:middle line:90%
because those stories are over.

00:06:38.720 --> 00:06:40.940 align:middle line:90%
So take notes.

00:06:40.940 --> 00:06:42.740 align:middle line:90%
Take notes.

00:06:42.740 --> 00:06:48.020 align:middle line:84%
Because what is happening around
