00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:14.630 align:middle line:84%
And you know what makes
us vulnerable right now?

00:08:14.630 --> 00:08:15.830 align:middle line:90%
And we are.

00:08:15.830 --> 00:08:19.680 align:middle line:10%
We're spiritually
