00:09:34.210 --> 00:09:35.670 align:middle line:90%
It's a crisis.

00:09:35.670 --> 00:09:39.390 align:middle line:84%
Because deep inside
of you, deep in you,

00:09:39.390 --> 00:09:41.520 align:middle line:90%
