00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:54.120 align:middle line:84%
You are wired to look for
awe, to be struck with awe.

00:09:54.120 --> 00:09:56.470 align:middle line:84%
You are absolutely
wired that way.

00:09:56.470 --> 00:10:01.860 align:middle line:84%
So here we find ourselves in
this collective crisis of god.

00:10:01.860 --> 00:10:04.530 align:middle line:90%
This is the era of the soul.

00:10:04.530 --> 00:10:12.290 align:middle line:84%
Up until this time, the idea
of our deeper consciousness

00:10:12.290 --> 00:10:14.330 align:middle line:84%
