00:10:45.450 --> 00:10:46.880 align:middle line:90%
They didn't do that.

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:49.410 align:middle line:90%
Now, think about what you do.

00:10:49.410 --> 00:10:51.210 align:middle line:10%
You ask those questions.

00:10:51.210 --> 00:10:54.360 align:middle line:84%
You think nothing
of saying, you know,

00:10:54.360 --> 00:10:56.966 align:middle line:90%
