00:10:56.966 --> 00:11:00.570 align:middle line:10%
It doesn't even occur
to you not to ask that.

00:11:00.570 --> 00:11:01.950 align:middle line:90%
Not at all.

00:11:01.950 --> 00:11:06.540 align:middle line:84%
For you, going in the
world behind your eye

00:11:06.540 --> 00:11:08.310 align:middle line:90%
