00:11:08.310 --> 00:11:14.830 align:middle line:84%
For you, the inner frontier
is the new frontier.

00:11:14.830 --> 00:11:20.600 align:middle line:84%
Going into the soul has
become the new normal.

00:11:20.600 --> 00:11:28.120 align:middle line:10%
But the old idea of god does
not work for the depth charges

00:11:28.120 --> 00:11:34.330 align:middle line:10%
of how we need to understand
the nature of god that

00:11:34.330 --> 00:11:40.340 align:middle line:10%
matches what we're
discovering about the soul.

00:11:40.340 --> 00:11:43.290 align:middle line:84%
Now, I realize that
probably for most of you,

00:11:43.290 --> 00:11:46.220 align:middle line:84%
